### Tool manifest (agent startup)
GET http://localhost:4000/tools

###

### Search movies — Inception (2010)
POST http://localhost:4000/tools/search_movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Inception",
  "year": 2010
}

###

### Get movie details — Inception (TMDB id 27205)
POST http://localhost:4000/tools/get_movie_details
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movie_id": 27205
}

###

### Get similar movies — Inception (TMDB id 27205)
POST http://localhost:4000/tools/get_similar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movie_id": 27205
}
